captions.text: And I bet you a flower that you've watched TV at least once.
"Things are not like they used to."
Today I was surfing the internet and I found this picture.
Who takes a selfie like that?, it's like
I'm so sad, why did she leave me?.
Speaking of telescopes, have you noticed how everything changes?.
Nothing's like it used to be.
Before, to make a friend, you had to do something like this.
Me too!, do you wanna be my friend?.
Now the most common way of making friends is:
Sit on your desk, go to Facebook,
My mom used to tell me to be careful with strangers.
My mom used to say "Don't take candy from strangers".
that was the way to win a child's trust.
No, my mommy said I shouldn't go with strangers.
But if you come with me, I'll give you candy.
Hey, do you want to come with me kid?.
Before, my neighbors knocked my door for this:
May I borrow a cup of sugar?.
Now when my neighbor comes over it's for:
Hi neighbor!, can you give me your WiFi password?.
Damn neighbors that put passwords in their WiFi.
my mom used to ground me by telling me to go to my room.
She wouldn't let me go out, or see my friends.
If you tell a kid to go to their room,
you send him to damn heaven.
They have everything in their room.
Being young back then was very different from being young now.
And it's even more notorious if you're a girl.
For example I had a friend.
I'm not saying her name, to protect her.
One day this friend went to a party.
And drank a bit too much.
And the next day when she woke up.
Well, last night you fooled around with a guy.
My cell?!, I lost my cellphone!!.

NO!.
My cell?!, I lost my cellphone!!.
We live in a world where losing your cellphone
is more dramatic than losing your virginity.
But in comparison with before, yeah.
Besides everything now is like sexual.
Before, you listened to the radio and this is what you heard:
But now, you turn on the radio and hear:
"I'm gonna do you until the sun comes up".
Something that has changed a lot is the parent's authority.
Before, if you wanted to go out, you'd ask your mom or dad.
And if they said no, it was NO.
You hated your mom for the rest of the night but you didn't go out.
I'm gonna go out, I'm gonna drink,
gonna do drugs and have an orgy with 7 big dudes.
But dear what are you talking abo-
Remember when just 2 years ago I was just a
guy who made videos in his room?.
Look at me now!, now I'm a..
What do you have as a wallpaper on your computer?.
I have a horse with a duck face.
When I was little they used to hit me with a belt.
This was this week's video, if you liked it please click thumbs up down here.
If it's the first time you watch one of my videos and you liked it Subscribe!, I upload videos every friday.
And because last friday I couldn't upload a video,
this tuesday I'll upload an extra video.
So this tuesday don't forget to go my channel to watch the other video.
Don't forget to follow me on my sensual Facebook.
T shirt, Tee, Shirt, top, however they say it in your country.
Although I don't know if you can see it.
It looks better in the dark.
A psychological hug and see you next tuesday,
Because I love you and when I can't upload a video I try to give you an extra one.
If that's not love, I don't know what is.
I was gonna knock and I saw you weren't doing anything so I opened the door.
I need a computer, can I take this one?.
Wait let me erase the porn.
